**Authors:** [[*user Anorrack]]

**If you liked this, you would like:**

**[[[Dead Man Walking]]]:** In the finale to DEAD RECKONING, Quinn Law and the UIU race against time to stop the Lighthouse Mafia from staging the largest breakout in Paramax history.

**[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/greenlight GREENLIGHT]:** //Between them, two hundred and fifteen years of service, between them seven rifles, seven parachutes, seven shots of rum, between them one atomic bomb.//

