The world is at war.

North America is an island fortress. Europe descends into butchery and madness. The Soviet Union dies piecemeal in the countless millions. Asia and Africa are frontiers of disease, death, and desperate measures.

All while the Pacific burns.

Behind the Second World War, battles are waged in the shadows. A war of monsters and mages, demons and sages, where witchcraft and alchemy are as powerful as artillery and rifles. The Seventh Occult War rages beyond borders, between Allies and Axis alike. A bid to control the fate of man.


As the Germans attempt the apotheosis of an Aryan god and the British conduct secret experiments on their asteroid colony, the Japanese have their own plans, plans that may shift the balance of both wars and secure their stranglehold on the so-called "co-prosperity sphere" for good. The Allies must stop them at all costs, for the sake of the Veil and the entire world.

Enter: Taskforce Ruby Lockbox.
